，在井下时间说是规定八小时，但是经常九小时甚至十个多小时，在公司的话时间就是十二小时了，也是蛮烦恼的</p>\n<p>白班 8 点班在公司基本上是早上六点到，下午五点半或者六点走</p>\n<p>中班 4 点班是下午两点前到，第二天凌晨一点半或者两点走</p>\n<p>夜班 0 点班是晚上十点到，第二天早上九点半或十点走</p>\n<p>井下环境的话，的确幸苦，很多体力活，基本大家都是大学生，都要去做体力劳动的\n煤灰蛮多的，打水钻还好，风钻的话，满脸都是黑，口罩也没有用的</p>\n<img alt=\"d936f92d6d52a4114f03678bcd7f700\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/GdRzq3w/d936f92d6d52a4114f03678bcd7f700.jpg\" title=\"我的煤灰脸\"/>\n<p>感觉在北京的工作生活是一眼看不到未来，回来的生活是一眼望到未来吧，加油，兄弟们</p>\n", "last_modified": 1733653989, "replies": 211, "id": 1095904}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 65018, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9159, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 11122, "username": "wellhome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wellhome", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2bf0/ccdb/11122_mini.png?m=1608915346", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2bf0/ccdb/11122_normal.png?m=1608915346", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2bf0/ccdb/11122_large.png?m=1608915346", "created": 1313370118, "last_modified": 1608915346}, "last_reply_by": "herozzm", "last_touched": 1733731452, "title": "云计算革了运维的命, 现在大模型革了程序员的命", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1095988", "created": 1733706901, "deleted": 0, "content": "云计算 infra  as code, 迅速革了运维老哥们的命. 程序员说你们运维的活,我们 code 包了.\r\n运维老哥们含泪下岗, 为了一家老小只好去跑滴滴,美团饿了么. 风里雨里, 满鬓双白.\r\n结果这才几年不到, 大模型来了, 这些程序员也要被革了.\r\n只能说, 出来混,都是要还的. 苍天饶过谁, 除了资本家. \r\n攒钱买股权,才是正道. 可惜沉浸于技术, 知道的太晚.\r\n\r\n云计算的口号是让 server 像电一样, 人人都能用的上.\r\n大模型的口号是, 让编程像 cloud 一样, 人人都能用的上.", "content_rendered": "<p>云计算 infra  as code, 迅速革了运维老哥们的命. 程序员说你们运维的活,我们 code 包了.\n运维老哥们含泪下岗, 为了一家老小只好去跑滴滴,美团饿了么. 风里雨里, 满鬓双白.\n结果这才几年不到, 大模型来了, 这些程序员也要被革了.\n只能说, 出来混,都是要还的. 苍天饶过谁, 除了资本家.\n攒钱买股权,才是正道. 可惜沉浸于技术, 知道的太晚.</p>\n<p>云计算的口号是让 server 像电一样, 人人都能用的上.\n大模型的口号是, 让编程像 cloud 一样, 人人都能用的上.</p>\n", "last_modified": 1733707132, "replies": 112, "id": 1095988}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 226239, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4281, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 401806, "username": "sawyera", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sawyera", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5bc69b6ccf103a84ff956615907ee9d3?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5bc69b6ccf103a84ff956615907ee9d3?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5bc69b6ccf103a84ff956615907ee9d3?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1555299422, "last_modified": 1555299422}, "last_reply_by": "jixiangqd", "last_touched": 1733731106, "title": "现在麦当劳不提供堂食收餐服务了吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1095997", "created": 1733708677, "deleted": 0, "content": "印象里自 21 年开始就不提供堂食选项了，强制选中打包。门店贴着要求顾客自行清理垃圾的贴士，这真的合理么？", "content_rendered": "印象里自 21 年开始就不提供堂食选项了，强制选中打包。门店贴着要求顾客自行清理垃圾的贴士，这真的合理么？", "last_modified": 1733708677, "replies": 74, "id": 1095997}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_larg